5 781 M
(  }) s
5 770 M
(  namespace _Iso_c = _Iso_c_1989;) s
5 748 M
(The alias allows later revisions of the standard to be adopted as the) s
5 737 M
(default, as is likely for the case of ISO C.  Names from previous) s
5 726 M
(standards can be adopted into each subsequent version, or shadowed.) s
5 715 M
(We can further recommend that preprocessor macros in C standards that) s
5 704 M
(can usefully be defined as properly-scoped C++ constants or inline) s
5 693 M
(functions should be.) s
5 671 M
(Of course, the above is just an example; details of the recommended) s
5 660 M
(pattern will be worked out more fully in the proposal for the technical) s
5 649 M
(report text.  This proposal is simply for the committee to resolve to) s
5 638 M
(publish a technical report as outlined above, and to request a detailed) s
5 627 M
(proposal of its contents.) s
_R
S
